{"tid":1751473,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"我之前是在票站打工的...","createTime":"2019-11-24T17:25:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-26T02:09:36.000Z","uid":62750,"like":14,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"dd0e8aca2999a0d8559005deff79381cd9d01481","tid":1751473,"uid":62750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T17:25:27.000Z","msg":"我之前是在票站打工的，而我點票的原則是：<br />\n「幹你娘點爆」<br />\n沒錯，就是幹你娘點爆，老子才不管甚麼建制派虧損三小的，每次點的非建派票就是姬芭一大堆。落後點成領先，領先點成全票當選。本土派買一送一，跟把整個票站的選票全送給非建制沒兩樣。<br />\n<br />\n我還記得，我那屆上班25小時，票站主任跑來跟我說，這屆建制派損失二百六十席，你有頭緒嗎？<br />\n<br />\n我他媽的怎麼會知道。"},{"pid":"f2b4c39c2800acd9b65b976561c509473a91383d","tid":1751473,"uid":142358,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T17:26:02.000Z","msg":"非常無聊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"318fff6dcf80b26b3c6c3d4c5e5f928f05d92719","tid":1751473,"uid":22231,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f2b4c39c2800acd9b65b976561c509473a91383d","tid":1751473,"uid":142358,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T17:26:02.000Z","msg":"非常無聊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T17:26:25.000Z","msg":"拉"},{"pid":"826735c0c9151da1942f7ab1a88995848926969b","tid":1751473,"uid":149607,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T17:27:09.000Z","msg":"非常無聊"},{"pid":"5896e5fbd145d00984026a7da4c7237c375b5a64","tid":1751473,"uid":62750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T02:09:36.000Z","msg":"你估多左廿席"}]}